- Brand: FIJICAB (FIJI in black, CAB in green #10b981)
- Primary Color: Blue (#0A84FF)
- Secondary Color: Emerald Green (#10b981)
- Font: Plus Jakarta Sans (Google Fonts)
- Style: Luxury Minimalism (Inspired by Uber, Bolt, Tesla, Apple)
- Target: Tourists and locals in Fiji Islands
- Service: Ride-hailing platform (like Uber for Fiji)

## PROJECT STRUCTURE
- Tech Stack: Next.js 15 (App Router), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS 4
- Deployment: Cloudflare Pages (Static Export)
- Email: Brevo Integration
- Icons: Heroicons 24/outline (strokeWidth={1.5})
- Design Tokens: lib/design-tokens.ts

