## ‚ùå STRICTLY FORBIDDEN

### 1. Real Client/Company Names
- NO real client names without written permission
- NO identifiable project names in case studies
- Use: "a manufacturing company", "e-commerce platform"
- ‚úÖ FIJI CAB CONNECT is approved (it's OUR client)

### 2. Numbers & Metrics (ALL NUMBERS FORBIDDEN)
**EXAMPLES FROM THIS PROJECT (FIXED):**
- ‚ùå "50+ drivers" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Many professional drivers" or "Growing community"
- ‚ùå "24/7" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Always available" or "Always"
- ‚ùå "100% safe" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Fully safe and secure"
- ‚ùå "5 minute wait" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Fast connections" or "Quick response"
- ‚ùå "$0 fees" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Free to join" or "No joining fees"

**FORBIDDEN:**
- NO client counts ("500+ clients")
- NO years of experience ("Since 2000")
- NO team size ("100+ employees")
- NO metrics/percentages ("40% improvement", "100%")
- NO pricing/currency ("$50", "‚Çπ10,000", "FJD 3.00")
- NO time metrics ("24/7", "5 minutes")

**APPROVED ALTERNATIVES:**
- Use: "many", "experienced", "extensive", "always", "quickly", "fully"

### 3. Emojis (ZERO TOLERANCE)
**EXAMPLES FROM THIS PROJECT (FIXED):**
- ‚ùå üõ°Ô∏è ‚Üí ‚úÖ `<ShieldCheckIcon className="w-16 h-16 text-primary" strokeWidth={1.5} />`
