- ‚ùå üìç ‚Üí ‚úÖ `<MapPinIcon className="w-16 h-16 text-primary" strokeWidth={1.5} />`

**FORBIDDEN:**
- NO emojis in ANY visible content
- NO: üöÄ ‚ú® üí° ‚≠ê üéØ ‚ù§Ô∏è üî• üëç ‚úì ‚úÖ ‚ùå

**REQUIRED:**
- Use: Professional SVG icons from Heroicons only
- Import from: `@heroicons/react/24/outline`
- Style: `className="w-16 h-16 text-primary" strokeWidth={1.5}`

### 4. Pricing/Currency (FIJI-SPECIFIC)
**EXAMPLES FROM THIS PROJECT (FIXED):**
- ‚ùå "Base Fare: FJD 3.00" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Base Fare: Starting rate for every trip"
- ‚ùå "Per Kilometer: FJD 2.50" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Per Kilometer: Standard distance-based rate"
- ‚ùå "Estimated Fare: FJD 38.50" ‚Üí ‚úÖ "Get Your Fare Estimate" (CTA button)

**FORBIDDEN:**
- NO specific prices (FJD, USD, $, ‚Çπ)
- NO fare calculations or examples

**APPROVED:**
- Generic descriptions: "Competitive rates", "Fair pricing"
- CTAs: "Request Fare Quote", "Contact for rates"

### 5. Certification & Compliance Claims
- NO: ISO, SOC, HIPAA, PCI, GDPR certifications
- NO: "Certified", "Compliant", "Standards"
- NO: Regulatory claims or badges
- Use: "Industry best practices", "Professional standards"

### 6. Outcome-Based Case Studies
- NO client names in case studies
- NO specific outcomes/results
- NO before/after comparisons
- NO ROI or performance metrics
- Use: Process-focused descriptions, technology approach

### 7. Superlatives & Marketing Hype
- NO: "Best", "#1", "Leading", "World-class", "First" (unless factually true)
- NO: "Award-winning" without actual awards
- NO: Empty marketing fluff
- Use: "Experienced", "Professional", "Trusted"
- ‚úÖ "Fiji's first cab-hailing platform" is approved (factually true)

### 8. Numbered Visual Elements
- NO numbered badges (01, 02, 03...)
- NO letters as design elements (A, B, C...)
- Use: Meaningful SVG icons only


# ---------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED FEATURES (MUST IMPLEMENT)
# ---------------------------------------------------------

## ‚úÖ Technical Requirements

### 1. Mobile-First Responsive
- Test on: 375px (mobile), 768px (tablet), 1280px (desktop)
- Use Tailwind: `text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl` pattern
- Touch targets minimum 44x44px
- FIJI-SPECIFIC: Hero images must work on mobile (test hero-1.png through hero-4.png)

### 2. Accessibility (WCAG AA)
- Skip to main content link (required)
- ARIA labels on interactive elements
- Semantic HTML (header, main, nav, footer)
- Keyboard navigation functional
- Color contrast ratio > 4.5:1
- Focus indicators visible
- ‚úÖ IMPLEMENTED: Header has skip link, all buttons have proper ARIA

### 3. SEO Metadata (Every Page)
- Title tag (50-60 characters)
- Meta description (150-160 characters)
- Canonical URL: https://fijicabconnect.com
- Open Graph tags
- Proper heading hierarchy (H1 ‚Üí H2 ‚Üí H3)
- ‚úÖ IMPLEMENTED: app/layout.tsx has complete metadata

### 4. Schema Markup (Approved Types Only)
‚úÖ ALLOWED:
- Organization (generic info only)
- WebPage (basic page info)
- Service (NO ratings/awards)
- BreadcrumbList (navigation)

‚ùå FORBIDDEN:
- AggregateRating
- Review
- Award
- Certification
- Any metrics (employee count, years, etc.)

### 5. Design System (FIJI CAB CONNECT)
- Design Tokens: lib/design-tokens.ts (MANDATORY reference)
- Primary Color: #0A84FF (blue)
- Secondary Color: #10b981 (emerald green)
- Accent: Use sparingly
- Typography: Plus Jakarta Sans (weights: 400, 500, 600, 700, 800)
- Icons: Heroicons (SVG, strokeWidth={1.5}) only
- Spacing: Tailwind scale (4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 16, 20, 24...)


# ---------------------------------------------------------
# FIJI CAB CONNECT COMPONENT PATTERNS
# ---------------------------------------------------------

## Icon Component Pattern (USE THIS):
```tsx
import { ShieldCheckIcon } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'

// In component:
const features = [
  {
    icon: ShieldCheckIcon,  // Store as component reference
    title: 'Verified Drivers',
    description: '...'
  }
]

// In render:
{features.map((feature, index) => {
  const Icon = feature.icon
  return (
    <div key={index}>
      <Icon className="w-16 h-16 text-primary" strokeWidth={1.5} />
      <h3>{feature.title}</h3>
      <p>{feature.description}</p>
    </div>
  )
})}
```

## Color Usage Pattern:
- `text-primary` - Blue accent text (#0A84FF)
- `bg-primary` - Blue backgrounds
- `text-black` - Main headings (use sparingly)
- `text-white` - Dark backgrounds
- `text-gray-600` - Body text
- Emerald green (#10b981) - "CAB" in logo, accents

## Typography Pattern:
- Hero: `text-7xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl font-black`
- Section Heading: `text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-black`
- Subsection: `text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black`
- Body Large: `text-2xl md:text-3xl font-light`
- Body: `text-lg leading-relaxed`


