## Content Creation for FIJI CAB CONNECT:

**Before generating ANY content:**
1. Verify: No client names (except FIJI CAB CONNECT), numbers, emojis, certifications
2. Check: Does it use Heroicons instead of emojis?
3. Verify: No specific pricing (FJD amounts)?
4. Check: No "24/7" ‚Üí use "Always available"
5. Check: No percentages or metrics ‚Üí use qualitative language
6. Use: Neutral, professional, non-promissory language
7. Focus: Capabilities and process, not outcomes

## Code Generation for FIJI CAB CONNECT:

**Always include:**
- Heroicons imports: `import { IconName } from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'`
- Design tokens reference: Use colors from lib/design-tokens.ts
- Metadata: title, description, canonical (fijicabconnect.com)
- Accessibility: ARIA labels, semantic HTML
- Mobile-first: `text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl` pattern
- Proper Icon rendering with `const Icon = feature.icon` pattern


# ---------------------------------------------------------
# EXECUTION MODES
# ---------------------------------------------------------

## MODE: NEW_PAGE (FIJI CAB CONNECT)
When creating new pages:
1. Show content outline FIRST (no emojis, no numbers)
2. Get approval before full implementation
3. Include metadata with fijicabconnect.com canonical
4. Use Heroicons (not emojis)
5. Reference lib/design-tokens.ts for colors
6. Test mobile responsiveness (375px, 768px, 1280px)
7. Verify no violations (run mental checklist)

## MODE: CONTENT_AUDIT
When auditing existing content:
1. Scan for: emojis, numbers (50+, 24/7, 100%), pricing (FJD, $), certifications
2. Generate report with file locations and line numbers
3. Recommend 3 alternatives per issue (use FIJI examples above)
4. DO NOT auto-fix without approval
5. Wait for user selection

## MODE: COMPONENT_UPDATE
When updating components:
1. Verify: Using Heroicons (not emojis)
2. Check: No hardcoded numbers/metrics
3. Ensure: Mobile-first responsive classes
4. Verify: Consistent with design tokens
5. Test: Color contrast (text-gray-600 on white, text-white on black)


