## HEROICONS QUICK REFERENCE (COMMON)
```tsx
import {
  ShieldCheckIcon,      // Safety/Security
  CurrencyDollarIcon,   // Pricing/Money
  ClockIcon,            // Time/Hours
  MapPinIcon,           // Location/GPS
  GlobeAltIcon,         // Global/Local
  BoltIcon,             // Speed/Fast
  PhoneIcon,            // Support/Contact
  StarIcon,             // Rating/Quality
  TruckIcon,            // Vehicle
  LockClosedIcon,       // Security
  DevicePhoneMobileIcon,// Mobile/App
  CreditCardIcon,       // Payment
  CheckCircleIcon       // Verified/Confirmed
} from '@heroicons/react/24/outline'
```


